<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erro de Autenticação - Lumi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-purple-900 to-violet-900 min-h-screen">

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
                <i class="fab fa-discord text-white text-5xl"></i>
            </div>
            
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4">OAuth Error</h1>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white/80 mb-6">Problema na Autenticação Discord</h2>
                <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-8">
                    A URL de callback do Discord OAuth precisa ser configurada. Isso é um problema temporário de configuração.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-left">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-tools mr-2 text-orange-400"></i>
                    Como Resolver:
                </h3>
                <ol class="text-white/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
                    <li><strong>1.</strong> Acesse: <a href="https://discord.com/developers/applications" target="_blank" class="text-purple-300 hover:text-purple-200">Discord Developer Portal</a></li>
                    <li><strong>2.</strong> Selecione a aplicação "Lumi"</li>
                    <li><strong>3.</strong> Vá em OAuth2 → Redirects</li>
                    <li><strong>4.</strong> Adicione esta URL:</li>
                </ol>
                <div class="mt-3 p-3 bg-black/20 rounded-lg">
                    <code class="text-green-300 text-xs break-all">
                        https://ac9d1766-758d-46a5-a5d1-7c3902e58581-00-1pz0zvgkhy08i.kirk.replit.dev/auth/discord/callback
                    </code>
                </div>
                <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mt-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock mr-1"></i>
                    Aguarde até 10 minutos após salvar no Discord.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <a href="/" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-violet-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-violet-600 transition-all font-semibold">
                    <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i>
                    Voltar ao Início
                </a>
                <button onclick="window.location.reload()" class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/20 transition-all font-semibold">
                    <i class="fas fa-sync-alt mr-2"></i>
                    Tentar Novamente
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">
                <p>Para suporte técnico: <a href="/support" class="text-purple-300 hover:text-purple-200">clique aqui</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>